      "text": "1. **Destructive Operations Prohibited**: Any git rollback operations like `git reset --hard` are **strictly prohibited** in any circumstances within a portal or the runtime workspace. Rollbacks must be handled through safe mechanisms (e.g., `git restore` on specific files or deleting the temporary worktree/branch) that do not risk deleting uncommitted or unrelated work.\n\n1.\n\n## Recommended Fix\n\n1. **Pass Repo Path**: Ensure `PlanExecutor` and `ExecutionLoop` always receive and pass the explicit portal repository path when creating `GitService`.\n\n1.\n1.\n\n## Fix Plan",
